               <bibl>ms Damas, Patriarcat syrien orthodoxe, cod. 12/17 (olim ms Dayr az-Za‘faran, cod. parch. 18 (Dolabany)), f. 106-107 ?</bibl>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="en" type="MSS" source="#bib1646-1">
